you only pay for what you use 
what is  client -server model ? 
you just learned more about AWS and how almost all of modern computing uses a basic client-server model 
let recap what a client-server model is 
client <-> server 
in computing  a client can be a web browser or desktop application that a person interacts with to make requests to computers servers 
a server can be services such as AMAZON ELASTIC COMPUTE CLOUD ( AMAZON EC2 ), A type of virtual server 

for example , suppose that a client makes a request for a news articles , the score is an online game or a funny video . The server evaluates the details of this requests and 
fulfills it by returning the information to the client .
